{"type":"message","id":"4fb2c569","parentId":"511aa5aa","timestamp":"2026-03-21T01:36:38.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Brew 命令不可用，这是 Windows 系统，brew 是 macOS 特有的工具，需要向用户报告这个情况并说明无法继续安装。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"brew 在此系统上不可用。这是 Windows 系统（DESKTOP-6U27CU7），而 brew（Homebrew）是 macOS/Linux 的包管理器。\n\n**任务结果：**\n- ❌ brew 不可用 - 系统是 Windows，brew 是 macOS/Linux 专用工具\n- ❌ 无法执行 `brew install steipete/tap/summarize`\n- ❌ 无法验证安装\n\n**建议：**\n如果需要在 Windows 上使用 summarize 工具，可以：\n1. 使用 WSL2（Windows Subsystem for Linux）安装 Linux 环境后再使用 brew\n2. 或者寻找 Windows 原生的替代方案"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774056994646}}
